talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"That's right. It's full of notes about fleeting sentiments. I thought it might prove useful someday for writing songs.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"One can never know when a fleeting moment will present itself in daily life, after all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"That's amazing, Kaoru! Okay, let's use that to think up some melodies and lyrics.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"episode190-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"Hagumi","body":"Yeah, let's do it~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"episode190-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Thank you, both of you. Your words make me happy.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"This is basically a song for you, after all, Kaoru. Now, tell us about your notes!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"episode190-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"Hagumi","body":"Yeah! When I think of fleeting, I think of Kaoru-kun!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"episode190-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Well, in this fleeting theme song... I would like to express a multitude of fleeting sentiments.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Why don't we start by going through each of my past fleeting moments and make a melody for them?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"In the intro, I'd like to place emphasis on the power of fleetingness and strike a powerful beat. Oh, that itself is fleeting...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"Hagumi","body":"I've got a feeling this is gonna be awesome!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"episode190-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"And then the first verse will be quiet, expressing a fleeting sensation through a lonely melody... Ahh, fleeting again...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"And then, in the chorus... We will display the intense passion of fleetingness, like a roaring fire...  Ahh, how fleeting this is...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode190-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"I think this is going to be a really fun song!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"episode190-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Fufu, it makes me happy to hear that. I want to use these notes and create a song that only we can create.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}